name: Sigma Essential Kit
description:
The Sigma Beauty Essential Kit was specially designed for a fun yet functional makeup application. This kit contains twelve colorful brushes from our best-selling Essential Kit. The brushes come in an innovative and functional container that turns into two brush holders to keep you stylish and organized.
 

Brushes Included:
 
E05 - Eye Liner: Create smooth and even lines. Use with gel or liquid liners.
E30 - Pencil: Soften and smoke out lines. Soften pencil liners along the top and bottom lash lines, add shadow to line the eyes, or use to highlight inner corner of eyes.
E40 - Tapered Blending: Soft blended crease. Using just the tips to apply color, sweep back and forth through the crease for a diffused and blended finish.
E55 - Eye Shading: Even application of color. Place color across the whole lid for an even and strong application of product.
E60 - Large Shader: Uniformly cover the whole lid with product. Apply cream shadow base or cream shadow for quick and even coverage.
E65 - Small Angle: Create precise lining. Moves fluidly and easily across the upper and lower lash lines. Use with gel, cream or powder liners.
E70 - Medium Angled Shading: Soft application of color. Use for brow highlighting or to blend the crease.
F30 - Large Powder: Even powder application. Uniform blending of powder products onto the face and body.
F40 - Large Angled Contour: Subtle cheek application. Use the angle to softly contour the cheekbone. Can also be used to apply blush.
F50 - Duo Fibre: Creates an airbrush effect onto the skin. Can be used with powder, liquid or cream products.
F60 - Foundation: Smooth foundation application. Apply liquid or cream products such as foundation and primer.
F70 - Concealer: Conceal small areas. Conceal the hardest to reach areas such as around the nose and eyes.

F40 - Large Angled Contour: Subtle cheek application. Use the angle to softly contour the cheekbone. Can also be used to apply blush.

description:
Everybody wants to get the best out of their spray tan so our kaftan dresses have a few little extra features to make your spray tanning experience as easy and convenient as possible.
We wanted something that everybody could wear with ease, so we designed our kaftan dresses for function but also considered fashion in our design to enable you to feel confident in and out of the salon and/or at home.

Made from a prewashed rayon blend the fabric feel is soft and smooth against the skin. It is lightweight and designed for comfort and thick enough for appropriate cover. The neckline has an extra wide cut and a heat printed label to keep the garment as seamless as possible.

There will be a range of vibrant colours and on trend fabric patterns and collections that we will bring you as the seasons change. The best thing about our kaftan dresses is that they are also very versatile in that they can be worn from tan to lunch, to the beach or even from poolsides to cocktails!

So effortlessly easy and playful to wear they can be the perfect compliment for any occasion and can be super-cool, super-cute or super-chic!

description:

With anti-oxidants, vitamins A and E, Green Tea and Grape Seed extract, this weightless oil-free primer fills in fine lines and wrinkles, prevents collagen breakdown and gives the skin a silky smooth, long lasting, flawless base.

Tahitian Glow and Monaco Matte are our Tinted Primers which act exactly as the 4 core primers however gives a bronzed tint. Available in Tahition Glow which has a shimmer and Monaco Matte which is a matte finish with no shimmer. Great for quick applications and out the door.

name: TanGO Glove
description:
You loved tanGO® the WORLD’s FIRST tan removal cloth for it’s ease of use and effectiveness. Now Tanology has harnessed the technology behind the revolutionary cloth to produce tanGO® tan removal glove!

Presented in its very own convenient canister, the cute pink tanGO® tan removal glove works just like the original tanGO® cloth, but in glove form! The elasticised band means the glove won’t slip when you’re sloughing off tanning build-up or errors.

tanGO® tan removal glove features the same special weave of fabric first  released in the original cloth. The weave acts like elastic, gently pulling the tanning pigment away from the skin without the use of any harsh exfoliants or chemicals.

tanGO® tan removal glove is super soft yet has amazing quality when it comes to removing tanning pigment. There are no hidden chemicals or additives in tanGO®. Just like the cloth, it’s as simple as Wet Me. Squeeze Me. Rub Me.!,

States tanGO® creator Jodi Bibra, “I love to use my glove with my favourite shower gel. The wetter your tanGO® tan removal glove the less tan it will remove so you can use it as a blending tool half way through your tan, then squeeze it a little more at the end of your tan to remove build up. “

“In other words, it’s a one stop product for pre-tan preparation and during & post-tanning maintenance.”

name: TanGO Cloth
description:
tanGO® is the world’s first spray and self tan removal cloth….NO harsh chemicals, just add water. tanGO® removes tanning errors and helps keep your tan looking perfect for longer 

tanGO® is the perfect solution we have all been waiting for. It is as easy as WET ME, SQUEEZE ME, RUB ME. No more orange hands and feet, just a perfect flawless tan.

tanGO® is a specially formulated polyamide cloth, which gently removes the tanning pigment from the surface of your skin without all the harsh scrubbing or the use of chemicals. Perfect for use with self tan or spray tans.

name: Mineral Liquid Foundation SPF10
description:
A light-reflecting mineral foundation in a liquid form,  that feels like a second skin, resulting in a hydrated, flawless complexion.  Ultra gentle formula for all skin types, it  contains no irritants such as talc, bismuth oxychloride, preservatives, fragrance, nano-particles or FD&C dyes.

Light reflective properties diffuse flaws and imperfections including fine line and wrinkles, and give a flawless, airbrushed finish to cover, conceal and
correct all complexions.

For greater coverage, dust Mineral Powder Foundation over the top, or finish with a light spray of the Mineral Airbrush Foundation.

name: Kabuki Brush
description: Stunning crystal encrusted Kabuki brush - your essential tool to flawlessly buff mineral powder onto the skin. Super soft Taklon fibres create an airbrushed effect for complexion perfection. Can be used with powder foundation, blush and bronzer.

name: Mineral Powder Foundation SPF15
description:
A favorite amongst A-list celebrities, this weightless "second skin" micronised mineral formula is a foundation, concealer, powder and chemical free SPF 15 all in one.  Ultra gentle for all skin types, it's hypo-allergenic non-chalky formula contains no irritants such as talc, bismuth oxychloride, preservatives, fragrance, nano-particles or FD&C dyes. Containing luxurious pearl powder and olive squalene for it's potent anti-aging benefits (natures own face lift).
Light reflective properties diffuse flaws and imperfections including fine line and wrinkles, and give a flawless, airbrushed finish to cover, conceal and
correct all complexions. 

Providing naturally water resistant coverage that lasts all day and won't crease, fade or wear away. Undiluted and pure, very little is needed to achieve great coverage, a 20g jar lasting approx 6 months of everyday use.

name: Velocity Rapid 1hr Self-Tan Mist
description: Introducing the first rapid 1 hour self tan. Velocity is the world's quickest, darkest, longest lasting rapid tan. Wash and wear in as little as 1 hour!* Our exclusive high performance spa formula contains Quad Bronzing Technology, Australian Kakadu Plum, Quandong, Aloe Vera and Vitamins A & E, for potent anti-aging and skin firming properties. A natural based formula that contains no parabens, mineral oils, artificial fragrance, glycols, sulphates, petrochemicals DEA, or TEA.

name: Liquid Sun Self-Tan Mist
description: A favourite of leading celebrities, Liquid Sun provides sun-kissed perfection rich in anti-oxidants, botanical extracts and precious oils of argan, macadamia and coconut. It strengthens and reinforces skin tone and elasticity, whilst nourishing the skin. A natural based formula that contains no parabens, mineral oils, artificial fragrance, glycols, sulphates, petrochemicals DEA, or TEA.

name: Brazilian Bronze Self-Tan Mousse
description:
Brazilian Bronze is the ultimate in self tanning for those wanting a rich, ultra dark tan with ease of application of a velvety mousse - a guaranteed flawless, streak free tan in as little as 1 hour!

The lightweight formula infused with Aloe Vera and Cehami (Australian botanical) will provide an even, natural looking tan, whilst hydrating the skin. The potent anti-aging and skin firming properties of Quandong, Australian Kakadu Plum Extract (Vitamin C) and Vitamins A & E mean you are one step closer to younger, healthier looking skin with each application.

name: Bronzing Mitt
description:
An absolute must have for any self tanners! This reusable mitt allows you to easily apply and blend self tan for a professional streak free finish. This water resistant barrier will ensure your hands are kept stain free.

This unique mitt is especially designed for simple, non-messy and streak-free application of Vani-T's Brazilian Bronze Self Tan Mousse, Liquid Sun Medium Self Tan Mist and Velocity Rapid Self Tan Mist using the velvety side.

Simply hand wash with mild detergent to clean and reuse.


Tip for salons: The Bronzing Mitt can be used to buff and blend hands, wrists, feet, elbows and any other body part requiring blending when performing a professional spray tan service.

name: Bronzing Custard
description:
A celebrity favourite, this gradual self tanner cleverly combines serious skin care benefits with a healthy touch of bronze.  Now you can achieve a perfect red carpet glow, everytime. 

Effectively extending and boosting an existing tan, or to build a natural glow worthy of a red carpet appearance. At the same time, a unique blend of intense, hydrating oils and powerful antioxidants quench the skin's thirst, leaving it hydrated, fresh and radiant. Formulated with Marine Collagen extract, Aloe Vera, Vitamins A &E, and botanical oils to nourish and improve skin's elasticity, tone and texture.

name: Tan Eraser
description:
Vani-T's Tan Eraser is an exfoliating and tan removal mitt, made from 100% natural fibres which miraculously sloughs away dead skin cells easily and effortlessly. Fantastic for removing a faux tan, or just for the silkiest skin ever.


Remember, pre-tan preparation is the key to the longevity and even fading of your spray tan.

 
The Tan Eraser is also perfect for assisting in cellulite reduction, minimising stretch marks and increasing circulation for radiant, glowing skin.
